{
  "entries": [
    {
      "offset": "0x162175",
      "back_en": "I can smell it anywhere.",
      "verdict": "revise",
      "note": "Omite 'wherever it lurks' (onde quer que se esconda)."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x16228c",
      "back_en": "Y-You knew about that too!?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Equivalente."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1623e2",
      "back_en": "You... will listen to my problems, then?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x16254a",
      "back_en": "my vassal, Oshtor.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correto."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x162659",
      "back_en": "man destined to be at my side one day.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Equivalente."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1626e5",
      "back_en": "not also harbor feelings for Oshtor?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x16270e",
      "back_en": "O-Of course not.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Stutter extra mas ok."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x16277c",
      "back_en": "will be mine alone.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x162a0e",
      "back_en": "suppose Oshtor p-possibly prefers... men?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Equivalente."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x162a84",
      "back_en": "My dear--I-I mean, Oshtor has no such tastes!",
      "verdict": "revise",
      "note": "'br--' (brother) perde a pista de 'irmão'; 'quer--' não revela o vínculo."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x162da7",
      "back_en": "express his feelings.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x16309a",
      "back_en": "kidnap me, and stage a fateful duel with Oshtor.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1631c4",
      "back_en": "If you want me to face Oshtor,",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Equivalente."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1633bc",
      "back_en": "Truly a flash of genius indeed. Munechika--",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x16349f",
      "back_en": "Besides that, to involve Lord Oshtor of the",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1634d0",
      "back_en": "Twin Shields in your plans? I cannot allow it.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Ponto extra, mas continua na linha seguinte; aceitável."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x163669",
      "back_en": "not for lack of trust in you, but...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1639f5",
      "back_en": "secret...?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correto."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x163ac6",
      "back_en": "the person she loves at the first difficulty?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'she' implícito; aceitável."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x163d59",
      "back_en": "Fear not, for I have heard your pleas!",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Tom arcaico mantido."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x163db1",
      "back_en": "crawls into the room!",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x163dc7",
      "back_en": "Wh--!?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correto."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x163dfb",
      "back_en": "heart--I shall help you in your plea!",
      "verdict": "revise",
      "note": "'plight' (situação difícil) virou 'apelo' (plea)."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x16402c",
      "back_en": "to help a lovesick maiden!",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x16424a",
      "back_en": "I can't simply tell them the true",
      "verdict": "revise",
      "note": "'princess's' omitido; reorganização gera redundância com 've--'."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x16427a",
      "back_en": "identity tr--",
      "verdict": "revise",
      "note": "Corte fica estranho ('identidade ve--'); reorganização confusa do par de linhas."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x16428a",
      "back_en": "...Wait.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correto."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x164293",
      "back_en": "...if this guy works with Oshtor, then...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1642bd",
      "back_en": "You already know, don't you?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correto."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1642f8",
      "back_en": "Don't pretend with me. I'm talking about the",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'play dumb' bem rendido."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x16432f",
      "back_en": "I'm certain I know nothing about Her Highness",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x16435f",
      "back_en": "seeking refuge here.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1644b9",
      "back_en": "The matter is irrelevant, I believe it is now too late.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'Beside the point' aceitável."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1644e9",
      "back_en": "Huh...? Wh--When did they--",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correto."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x164719",
      "back_en": "I look forward to seeing what you do...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x164878",
      "back_en": "before word reaches Oshtor.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Equivalente."
    }
  ],
  "reviewed": 36
}